{"url": "https://people.com/parents/katie-lowes-adam-shapiro-welcome-son-albee/", "text": "Motherhood? It\u2019s handled.\n\nScandal star Katie Lowes announced the birth of her first child, son Albee on social media Thursday, which also happened to be the final season premiere of the ABC drama.\n\n\u201cBaby\u2019s first #Scandal live tweet! Adam and I are thrilled to welcome Albee Shapiro into our family! We\u2019re happy & healthy!\u201d the new mom shared on Twitter and Instagram.\n\nLowes announced her pregnancy with husband Adam Shapiro in May, joking to Jimmy Kimmel that the then-parents-to-be \u2014 who wed in 2012 \u2014 had \u201czero names\u201d in mind for their son on the way.\n\nWant all the latest pregnancy and birth announcements, plus celebrity mom blogs? Click here to get those and more in the PEOPLE Babies newsletter.\n\nThe actress previously revealed her birth plan for the October cover story of Fit Pregnancy and Baby, explaining, \u201cI wanted a doula because it\u2019s my first baby and I want to be able to call her when I\u2019m going into labor so she can come over and help us go through the early stage.\u201d\n\nShe added, \u201cMy husband and I are both actors; we\u2019re obviously dramatic. So we want someone who is able to say, \u2018This is normal. You\u2019re okay; let\u2019s do another lap around the house. Let\u2019s bounce on a ball, let\u2019s walk down the street.\u2019 \u201d\n\nRELATED VIDEO: Scandal\u2018s Katie Lowes Describes Kerry Washington in Three Words\n\nLowes, 36, explained to Fit Pregnancy and Baby that she doesn\u2019t want to \u201crush to the hospital too soon\u201d \u2013 not until she\u2019s \u201cofficially freaked out.\u201d\n\n\u201cBut [the doula will] be there as our advocate and as someone who has gone through this many more times than we have,\u201d she added.\n\nAhead of their baby\u2019s arrival, Lowes said she only had one wish: \u201cNow more than ever, to just please let my son be healthy and happy and safe. That\u2019s all that matters.\u201d", "images": ["https://people.com/thmb/xugQGctnmA9cRzQWEQv-mZA77Tg=/282x188/filters:no_upscale():max_bytes(150000):strip_icc():focal(560x165:562x167)/Ashley-Graham-3e7a7fae35c8476587b8a1793230a32f.jpg", "https://people.com/thmb/pD1ieYNLwkHRkjz70DYpiVPUQyM=/282x188/filters:no_upscale():max_bytes(150000):strip_icc():focal(734x339:736x341)/kristen-bell-katie-lowes-545e198df3fb4cb4af3a0da337017982.jpg", "https://people.com/thmb/ekfvYtCPwWYDWY-lIm6HlZRuxxA=/282x188/filters:no_upscale():max_bytes(150000):strip_icc():focal(749x0:751x2)/katie-lowes-a85f2051360a41ad869d3efe98e33ff7.jpg", "https://people.com/thmb/Lje7sGaj3HgeS-yLg9z5JSNPfrU=/300x150/filters:no_upscale():max_bytes(150000):strip_icc()/people_magazine_sub-e6689738996d40f38f154099e1751481.png", "https://people.com/thmb/SNHR7U6NtPhIzEzxN7X-UDCUn-k=/282x188/filters:no_upscale():max_bytes(150000):strip_icc():focal(652x619:654x621)/gettyimages-1144525710-2000-2f742935d89344a6969db85cb3d4395e.jpg", "https://people.com/thmb/M-aV34kA892Cu-38j1om75BDLww=/282x188/filters:no_upscale():max_bytes(150000):strip_icc():focal(999x0:1001x2)/lw-17-08-26-578-dw-2000-251eec4d0199448f8326946457d42444.jpg", "https://people.com/thmb/SJoOIxd_goodOKhHGwq7cDiPAww=/282x188/filters:no_upscale():max_bytes(150000):strip_icc():focal(999x0:1001x2)/katie-lowes-3-8577ac002eec4511bf423bc459060ee4.jpg", "https://people.com/thmb/BhTWGvPiWY8zlKC7wERKQilbXso=/282x188/filters:no_upscale():max_bytes(150000):strip_icc():focal(665x0:667x2)/lowes-shapiro-3-2000-18cb2889fc0d4d119f9c716065792dd2.jpg", "https://people.com/thmb/vYWg5KDRttJcSGUUOC-_i9Sw5tg=/1333x2000/filters:fill(auto,1)/lowes-shapiro-2-2000-2ab4c7b20d2b4b7e88070cbc573d6de2.jpg", "https://people.com/thmb/6C1si9FuAEVMRL5BfzBVOikgtKU=/282x188/filters:no_upscale():max_bytes(150000):strip_icc():focal(852x0:854x2)/rob-dyrdek-baby-2000-de0d98e535ca42dab0404512922b55ad.jpg", "https://people.com/thmb/0j9lxl6yLifPGkfSv-6oEBaShoU=/282x188/filters:no_upscale():max